title: Ep 108 - Things Are Heating Up
description:
Todd, Nick, Digs and Bailey held down the fort today with comedian Jeff Oskay. They talked about goats, chickens, raccoons, hospitals, overpopulation, the CIA, remote viewing and they round-tabled some listener questions.

Follow Jeff Oskay @seenfunnier on Twitter / @jeffoskay on Instagram.
